  NOTABLE RULES and tournament constants:
  Rule 30 = KEY1 * KEY2 * KEY_SUM (chaotic)
  Rule 110 = KEY1 * KEY_SUM * 11 (Turing-complete)
  Rule 90 = KEY1 * KEY2 * KEY2 * KEY_SUM (Sierpinski, additive)
